<h1>Word of the Day 8/31/16 - 9/2/16</h1>
<h3>September 2<sup>nd</sup> 2016</h3>
  <dl>
    <dt>gaposis</dt>
      <dd>a noticeable gap or series of gaps, as between the fastened buttons or snaps on an overly tight garment.</dd>
  </dl>
